Millard School was a blast. I believe in you guys. You will have a beautiful tomorrow.

Millard. Many of you had questions about how to deal with people who say negative things about you. Remember that there will always be negative people, your job isn’t to focus on the negativity. Your job is to focus on the positive movement your life can have. Realize your potential. Arrive for your dreams. And believe that with hard work and self confidence you can accomplish anything you set your mind to and you will have a beautiful tomorrow.
